  "synopsis": "After his ordinary life came to an end in an accident, Minoru was reincarnated as an elf with a lifespan of 1000 years. Due to regrets of not doing anything in his previous life, he decides to leave his village and travel in order to leave a mark in his new world. However, the head of the elf clan imposes a certain trial...?!\n\nThis is a tale of a reincarnated elf's leisurely life and his journey to become a living legend.\n\n(Source: Comic Grast, translated)",
